{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 57,
  "title": "第五十七章（治邦）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "以正之邦。以畸用兵。以无事取天下。吾何以知亓然也？"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫：天下多忌諱，而民彌貧。民多利器，而邦滋昏。人多知，而奇物滋起。法物滋彰，而盜賊多有。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人之言曰：我无為而民自化。我好靜而民自正。我无事而民自富。我欲不欲而民自樸。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 25,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以，至也。天使正身之人，使有國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 25,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "奇，詐也。天使詐偽之人，使用兵也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 12,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以無事無為之人，使取天下為之主。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 25,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此，今也。老子言，我何以知天意然哉，以今日所見知。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下謂人主也。忌諱者防禁也。令煩則奸生，禁多則下詐，相殆故貧。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利器者，權也。民多權則視者眩於目，聽者惑於耳，上下不親，故國家昏亂。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人謂人君、百里諸侯也。多技巧，謂刻畫宮觀，雕琢章服，奇物滋起，下則化上，飾金鏤玉，文繡彩色日以滋甚。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "法物，好物也。珍好之物滋生彰著，則農事廢，飢寒並至，而盜賊多有也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "謂下事也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人言：我修道承天，無所改作，而民自化成也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 28,
          "end": 29
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人言：我好靜，不言不教，而民自忠正也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 38
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我無徭役徵召之事，民安其業故皆自富也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 41,
          "end": 41
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "我常無欲，去華文，微服飾，民則隨我為質樸也。聖人言：我修道守真，絕去六情，民自隨我而清也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 25,
          "end": 25
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以道治國則國平，以正治國則奇正起也，以無事則能取天下也。上章云：其取天下者，常以無事，及其有事，又不足以取天下也。故以正治國則不足以取天下，而以奇用兵也。夫以道治國，崇本以息末，以正治國，立辟以攻末，本不立而末淺，民無所及，故必至於奇用兵也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "利器，凡所以利己之器也。民强則國家弱。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "民多智慧則巧偽生，巧偽生則邪事起。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 44,
          "end": 44
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "立正欲以息邪，而奇兵用；多忌諱欲以恥貧，而民彌貧；利器欲以强國者也，而國愈昬多。皆舍本以治末，故以致此也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 41,
          "end": 41
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上之所欲，民從之速也。我之所欲，唯無欲而民亦無欲而自樸也。此四者，崇本以息末也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
